Articles.Content:
Hey I'm trying to download the kethane mod, but I can't find the latest version. I have the latest version of KSP (it updated a few days ago.)

If anyone knows a mod that works better than kethane please suggest it.

Thanks in advance

See this post for an unofficial patch to make Kethane work for 0.90.

You also might want to take a look at Karbonite for a potential "mod that works better;" they're both pretty much equal (though IMHO Karbonite+ is rather overpowered) but rather different. I personally prefer Karbonite but have nothing against Kethane.
